/examples/api_workflow/api_workflow_state/

# Anvil agent-team harness (M5/Phase 15 REL-02): never commit harness state into
# the library tree. These are tracked-or-untracked working artifacts of the
# multi-agent workflow, not part of the published module. Excluding them here
# stops a future `git add -A` from sweeping the harness into a release commit.
.planning/
.smtc/
.smtc-cache/
anvil
anvil-up
spawn/
ANVIL-TEAM.md
.mcp.json

# Local experiment sandbox (not part of the library)
playground/
.claude/

# TLC model-checker scratch output (timestamped run dirs under specs/)
specs/states/
